Sentencas: Solid oxide fuel cells with nano-sized Co1.5Mn1.5O4 (CMO) crystals infiltrated LSM-YSZ cathodes have been investigated using XRD, SEM, EIS and cell performance measurements.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide fuel cells with Co1.5Mn1.5O4 infiltrated (La,Sr)MnO3-yittria stabilized zirconia cathodes

Sentencas: 20 similar to 30 nm nanocrystals of Co1.5Mn1.5O4 are present on the surfaces of LSM and YSZ particles.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide fuel cells with Co1.5Mn1.5O4 infiltrated (La,Sr)MnO3-yittria stabilized zirconia cathodes

Sentencas: The infiltrated cells display more than 2 times higher power density than the non-infiltrated cell under 0.7 V at the same temperature in 600-700 degrees C.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide fuel cells with Co1.5Mn1.5O4 infiltrated (La,Sr)MnO3-yittria stabilized zirconia cathodes

Sentencas: The Co1.5Mn1.5O4 infiltration reduces both ohmic resistance and polarization resistance in the cells.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide fuel cells with Co1.5Mn1.5O4 infiltrated (La,Sr)MnO3-yittria stabilized zirconia cathodes

Sentencas: The distribution of relaxation times (DRT) analysis of the EIS data depicts that oxygen reduction process is greatly accelerated on the infiltrated cathode, which is attributed to high catalytic activity of nano-sized CMO crystals.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide fuel cells with Co1.5Mn1.5O4 infiltrated (La,Sr)MnO3-yittria stabilized zirconia cathodes
